                    <h3 class="section-heading">Protect your cards today</h3>
                    <p class="lead">
                        Counterfeits are getting better every year. But you can protect yourself against future counterfeits, by logging images of your valuable cards into the Vaultarch secure database today. <br><br>
                        Load high-definition mobile phone or camera images of your valuable cards into Vaultarch today. Then if you want to sell or trade them in the future, you can have the histories to prove that these particular cards existed today.<br><br>
                        When you hand over a card to its new owner, you can also hand over to them the digital history of the card, including its new ownership details. So the new owner will have the same protection that you did.<br><br>
                        Take action today and lock in the future value of your cards.
                    </p>
                </div>
