                    <h3 class="section-heading">Build card provenance</h3>
                    <p class="lead">
                        "Provenance": a record of ownership of a work of art or an antique, used as a guide to authenticity or quality.<br><br>
                        Once a card is registered, additional data can be added (e.g. descriptions of how the card was acquired, the card was sourced, original sales receipts, new images, etc).
                        This builds a picture of historical card ownership.<br><br>
                        These records help build confidence and security in the community.
                    </p>
